snippet.title: 3.7 Version PV - Sublime Spring - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
The ageless true Celestial Phoenix who resided in the Taixuan Mountain now exist solely for a mission entrusted by her friend. Fu Hua's S-rank PSY battlesuit [Azure Empyrea] makes a grand debut!

To track down the Nian Beast, the Celestial and Book of Fuxi visits the ancient Shenzhou village of Xanadu for traces. Spring event [Empyrean Legends] available!
